      • SEQBS

        static final String[] SEQBS
        1D String Array constants used for cleaner reading, identifies the loading file for Sequence icons. First entry is the de-highlighted icon, with the second being the highlighted icon

      • PKBS

        static final String[] PKBS
        1D String Array constants used for cleaner reading, identifies the basic keyboard folder for loading images

      • KBS

        static final String[][] KBS
        2D String Array constants used for cleaner reading, identifies the loading file for basic keyboard icons by row. Rows 0 and 10 are de-highlighted and highlighted respectively, with group 1-10 between

      • DEFBS

        static final String[] DEFBS
        1D String Array constants used for cleaner reading, identifies the loading files for the default key. First entry is the de-highlighted default icon, with the second being the highlighted default icon
